### ==================== EMAIL TESTING NOTES ====================
### 
### How to test emails:
### 1. Open this file in VS Code REST Client extension
### 2. Run each test endpoint in sequence
### 3. Check your email inbox for incoming emails
### 4. Verify email contains:
###    - Correct recipient
###    - Proper template rendering
###    - Correct data (names, dates, priorities)
###    - Working links pointing to https://taska-rho.vercel.app
###
### Expected Email Flows:
### 
### Registration → Welcome Email
### ├─ User signs up
### └─ Welcome email automatically sent
###
### Forgot Password → Password Reset Email
### ├─ User requests password reset
### └─ Email with OTP code sent (4 min expiry)
###    └─ User submits OTP + new password
###       └─ Password Reset Success email sent
###
### Task Assignment → Task Assigned Email
### ├─ Admin creates task for user
### └─ Email notification sent to assignee
###    ├─ Task title, description
###    ├─ Due date, priority
###    └─ Link to portal (https://taska-rho.vercel.app)
###
### Task Completion → Completion Email
### ├─ User marks task as completed
### └─ Celebratory email sent to user
###    ├─ Task name
###    ├─ Completion date
###    └─ Achievements/Streak hint
###
### Email Template Locations:
### - src/mail/templates/welcome.hbs
### - src/mail/templates/password-reset.hbs
### - src/mail/templates/password-reset-success.hbs
### - src/mail/templates/task-assigned.hbs
### - src/mail/templates/task-reminder.hbs
### - src/mail/templates/task-completed.hbs
### - src/mail/templates/login-notification.hbs
### - src/mail/templates/security-alert.hbs
###
### Troubleshooting:
### - Check .env file for MAIL_HOST, MAIL_USER, MAIL_PASSWORD
### - Verify Gmail account allows Less Secure Apps or use App Password
### - Check logs for "Failed to send email" messages
### - FRONTEND_URL determines email links destination
